{"tid":639946,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北京霧霾空氣直送倫敦　四城氣味免費體驗　英國藝術家盼促關注污染","createTime":"2018-04-24T02:06:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-24T04:58:08.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"93f610369d37fd24a650e79efc35352add37806b","tid":639946,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T02:06:25.000Z","msg":"英國倫敦薩默塞特府（Somerset House）廣場上，近日冒現四個透明半球體裝置，歡迎公眾入內參觀，讓你一次過體驗四個城市的氣味！<br />\n<br />\n適逢昨天是「世界地球日」，英國藝術家 Michael Pinsky 上周四起搭建透明裝置「Pollution Pods」，每個半球體營造一個城市的空氣味道。他特別選擇了中國北京、巴西聖保羅、印度新德里，與（可能係全歐洲）空氣最清新的挪威小島 Tautra 對比，從而刺激倫敦市民反思當地環境污染的問題。<br />\n<br />\n與丹麥空氣潔淨公司 Airlabs 合作，Pinsky 透過控制室內溫度、氣味等，從而模仿四個城市的空氣質素。根據參觀者的描述，聖保羅房間的乙醇含量高，令人忍不住流眼水；對比新德里令人窒息的氣味，北京的霧霾也不算甚麼；Tautra 房間的空氣則又輕又乾淨；離開裝置回到倫敦街頭，頓時察覺城內瀰漫著陣陣柴油惡臭。<br />\n<br />\nPinsky 解釋，人們早已看慣了北極融冰和沙漠中垂死孩子的影像，「但觀者只會感到無力，他們不知道可以怎樣幫忙」。因此，他希望透過體驗裝置，讓市民對比各地與倫敦的空氣質素，刺激他們自身生活開始改變，「必須讓觀者發現問題切身地影響自己，才可推動行為轉變。而我選擇倫敦做展覽，是因為在這裡我每日都感受到污染的問題」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DbJCcMYXcAA5i1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDbJCcMYXcAA5i1f.jpg&h=2b4cb427&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DbJFkJeWsAA4rrp?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDbJFkJeWsAA4rrp%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dsmall&d=4zss2oqrg8H8V9J5SRC0EE4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=53fd93d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DbJFkJeWsAA4rrp?format=jpg&amp;name=small</a><br />\n[/img]<br />\nElle Hunt<br />\n✔<br />\n@mlle_elle<br />\n Michael Pinsky&rsquo;s #PollutionPods, in the forecourt of Somerset House, claim to reproduce the air pollution conditions of five cities<br />\n<br />\n7:09 PM - Apr 19, 2018<br />\n24<br />\n18 people are talking about this<br />\nTwitter Ads info and privacy<br />\n<br />\nElle Hunt<br />\n✔<br />\n@mlle_elle<br />\n19 Apr<br />\nMichael Pinsky&rsquo;s #PollutionPods, in the forecourt of Somerset House, claim to reproduce the air pollution conditions of five cities <a href=\"http://pic.twitter.com/a6gwO4M8Hg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.twitter.com%2Fa6gwO4M8Hg&d=4zss2oqrg8H8V9J5SRC0EE4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=a99d67b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">pic.twitter.com/a6gwO4M8Hg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nElle Hunt<br />\n✔<br />\n@mlle_elle<br />\n Tautra, Norway. Low levels of nitrogen dioxide and particulate matter. The green light for outdoor sports and cycling. Almost a relief on entry <a href=\"http://pic.twitter.com/JYuLNJ83GK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.twitter.com%2FJYuLNJ83GK&d=4zss2oqrg8H8V9J5SRC0EE4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=90870d9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">pic.twitter.com/JYuLNJ83GK</a><br />\n<br />\n7:22 PM - Apr 19, 2018<br />\nView image on Twitter<br />\n3<br />\nSee Elle Hunt's other Tweets<br />\nTwitter Ads info and privacy<br />\n相關報道：<br />\n<br />\nGuardian／New York Times／Independent<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/art/%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E9%9C%A7%E9%9C%BE%E7%A9%BA%E6%B0%A3%E7%9B%B4%E9%80%81%E5%80%AB%E6%95%A6-%E5%9B%9B%E5%9F%8E%E6%B0%A3%E5%91%B3%E5%85%8D%E8%B2%BB%E9%AB%94%E9%A9%97-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E8%97%9D%E8%A1%93%E5%AE%B6%E7%9B%BC%E4%BF%83%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8%E6%B1%A1%E6%9F%93/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fart%2F%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E9%259C%25A7%25E9%259C%25BE%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E7%259B%25B4%25E9%2580%2581%25E5%2580%25AB%25E6%2595%25A6-%25E5%259B%259B%25E5%259F%258E%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E5%2591%25B3%25E5%2585%258D%25E8%25B2%25BB%25E9%25AB%2594%25E9%25A9%2597-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%2597%259D%25E8%25A1%2593%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E7%259B%25BC%25E4%25BF%2583%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%25B3%25A8%25E6%25B1%25A1%25E6%259F%2593%2F&d=4zss2oqrg8H8V9J5SRC0EE4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=03c1c616\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=h